%h2 Plan Categories
.flow-padding= button_to 'Create a new Plan Category', new_plan_category_path, :method => "get"
%p.notice
  Most Plan Categories should be shown on the Registration
  Form. However, the Congress Registration Plans are added
  automatically to each Attendee (based on age, etc.) so
  please do not show those plans on the Registration Form.

%table.semantic.fullwidth.zebra
  %thead
    %tr
      %th Category
      %th{:colspan=>3} Show on Which Pages?
      %th{:colspan=>3}      
    %tr.lesser-header
      %th
      %th Prices Page
      %th Room and Board Page
      %th Registration Form
      %th{:colspan=>3}
  %tbody
    - @plan_categories.each do |plan_category|
      %tr
        %td= plan_category.name
        %td= plan_category.show_on_prices_page ? "Yes" : "No"
        %td= plan_category.show_on_roomboard_page ? "Yes" : "No"
        %td= plan_category.show_on_reg_form ? "Yes" : "No"
        %td= link_to 'Details', plan_category
        %td= link_to 'Edit', edit_plan_category_path(plan_category)
        %td= link_to 'Delete', plan_category, :confirm => 'Are you sure?', :method => :delete

%br
